# Local-only secrets (never commit real values). Copy the lines you need:
#
#   cp .dev.vars.example .dev.vars
#
# `wrangler dev` loads `.dev.vars` and merges with `wrangler.jsonc` `vars`.
# With `wrangler dev --env development`, prefer `.dev.vars.development` for
# environment-specific secrets (if that file exists, the generic `.dev.vars` is not loaded).
#
# MIGRATION_TOKEN=
